---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | fitness-complete.com"
  description="Privacy policy for fitness-complete.com: what data we collect, how affiliate links work, and how to contact us."
>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <header class="border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">fitness-complete</a>
      <nav class="hidden sm:flex gap-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <a href="/gym-starter-set" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Gym</a>
        <a href="/pilates-starter-set" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Pilates</a>
        <a href="/running-starter-set" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Running</a>
        <a href="/home-gym-starter-set" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Home Gym</a>
        <a href="/boxing-starter-set" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Boxing</a>
        <a href="/gifts" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-medium text-gray-700">Gifts</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 pb-20">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors mb-6">← Home</a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-3">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-10">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">What data we collect</h2>
          <p>
            Fitness-complete.com does not collect personal data from visitors. We have no user accounts, no contact forms, no newsletter signups, and no checkout process. We do not store your name, email address, or any identifying information.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Standard server logs (including IP addresses and browser user-agent strings) may be retained by our hosting provider (Vercel) as part of normal infrastructure operation. We do not access or process these logs for marketing purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Affiliate disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            This site participates in affiliate programs, including Amazon Associates US and programs through Impact.com and other affiliate networks. When you click a product link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Affiliate relationships do not influence our product recommendations. Commission rate is never the reason a product is recommended on this site. See our <a href="/about" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">About page</a> for a full explanation of our methodology.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            This site is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cookies and analytics</h2>
          <p>
            We may use basic, privacy-respecting analytics to understand aggregate traffic patterns, such as which pages are visited most. If analytics are in use, they are configured to anonymize IP addresses and not track individual users across sessions or sites. We do not use advertising cookies or retargeting pixels.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            When the cookie banner appears, you can choose to Accept or Decline. If you choose Accept, basic anonymized analytics may be loaded. If you choose Decline, no analytics tracking is activated. Either choice dismisses the banner and stores your preference locally in your browser. You can clear this preference at any time by clearing your browser's local storage.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Third-party retailers linked from this site (Amazon, REI, Dick's Sporting Goods, etc.) have their own privacy policies and cookie practices. Once you navigate to a third-party site, their policies apply.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or anything else related to this site, you can reach us at <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">hello@fitness-complete.com</span>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>


</Layout>
